---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="왜 필리핀 어학연수? 장점·비용·효과 비교"
  description="1:1 집중 수업, 호주·캐나다 대비 1/3 비용. 필리핀 어학연수가 선택받는 이유와 스파르타·세미스파르타 차이점까지 총정리."
  path="/why-philippines"
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="pt-[140px] pb-16 px-6 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-green-badge text-accent-green-dark px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full text-[0.8rem] font-semibold mb-5 animate-fade-in-up">
        Why Philippines?
      </div>
      <h1
        class="text-[2rem] md:text-[3rem] font-black leading-[1.25] tracking-tight text-brown-dark animate-fade-in-up"
        style="animation-delay: 0.1s"
      >
        왜 <span class="text-terracotta">필리핀</span> 어학연수인가요?
      </h1>
      <p
        class="mt-5 text-[0.95rem] md:text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.7] text-brown animate-fade-in-up"
        style="animation-delay: 0.2s"
      >
        최소한의 비용으로 최대의 영어 실력 향상을 원한다면,<br />
        필리핀 어학연수가 정답입니다.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 탭 네비게이션 -->
  <div class="bg-white border-y border-beige-dark sticky top-16 z-30">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 flex gap-1 overflow-x-auto no-scrollbar">
      <a href="#section-0" class="shrink-0 px-4 py-3.5 text-[0.85rem] font-medium text-brown hover:text-terracotta hover:bg-terracotta-light/30 transition-colors no-underline rounded-t-lg">1:1 맨투맨 수업</a>
      <a href="#section-1" class="shrink-0 px-4 py-3.5 text-[0.85rem] font-medium text-brown hover:text-terracotta hover:bg-terracotta-light/30 transition-colors no-underline rounded-t-lg">스파르타 시스템</a>
      <a href="#section-2" class="shrink-0 px-4 py-3.5 text-[0.85rem] font-medium text-brown hover:text-terracotta hover:bg-terracotta-light/30 transition-colors no-underline rounded-t-lg">기숙형 어학원</a>
      <a href="#section-3" class="shrink-0 px-4 py-3.5 text-[0.85rem] font-medium text-brown hover:text-terracotta hover:bg-terracotta-light/30 transition-colors no-underline rounded-t-lg">합리적 비용</a>
      <a href="#section-4" class="shrink-0 px-4 py-3.5 text-[0.85rem] font-medium text-brown hover:text-terracotta hover:bg-terracotta-light/30 transition-colors no-underline rounded-t-lg">지리적 장점</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION 1: 1:1 맨투맨 수업 -->
  <section id="section-0" class="py-20 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-terracotta-light text-terracotta px-3 py-1.5 rounded-2xl text-[0.75rem] font-semibold mb-4">POINT 01</div>
        <h2 class="text-[1.6rem] md:text-[2.2rem] font-extrabold tracking-tight text-brown-dark leading-[1.3]">
          1:1 맨투맨 수업으로<br /><span class="text-terracotta">확실한 스피킹 향상</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-5 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] text-brown">
          필리핀 어학연수의 가장 큰 장점은 <strong>하루 4~6시간의 1:1 수업</strong>입니다. 서양권 어학연수는 대부분 10~15명 그룹 수업이라 말할 기회가 적지만, 필리핀에서는 선생님과 단둘이 수업하기 때문에 <strong>내성적인 성격이라도 영어를 말할 수밖에 없는 환경</strong>이 만들어집니다.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[0.9rem] text-brown leading-[1.6]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-green shrink-0 mt-0.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
            하루 4~6시간 1:1 수업 + 2~4시간 그룹 수업
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[0.9rem] text-brown leading-[1.6]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-green shrink-0 mt-0.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
            개인 레벨과 목표에 맞춘 커리큘럼
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[0.9rem] text-brown leading-[1.6]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-green shrink-0 mt-0.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
            선생님과 친밀한 관계 형성으로 학습 동기 유지
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[0.9rem] text-brown leading-[1.6]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-green shrink-0 mt-0.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
            내향적인 성격도 자연스럽게 스피킹 연습
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal rounded-[20px] aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524178232363-1fb2b075b655?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="1:1 맨투맨 영어 수업" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 2: 스파르타 시스템 -->
  <section id="section-1" class="py-20 px-6 bg-cream">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
      <div class="reveal text-center mb-14">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-terracotta-light text-terracotta px-3 py-1.5 rounded-2xl text-[0.75rem] font-semibold mb-4">POINT 02</div>
        <h2 class="text-[1.6rem] md:text-[2.2rem] font-extrabold tracking-tight text-brown-dark leading-[1.3]">
          나에게 맞는 <span class="text-terracotta">학습 스타일</span> 선택
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.7] text-brown max-w-[600px] mx-auto">
          필리핀 어학원은 학습 강도에 따라 3가지 타입으로 나뉩니다.<br />자신의 성향에 맞는 스타일을 선택할 수 있어요.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <!-- 스파르타 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-[20px] p-7 border border-terracotta/30 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <div class="inline-flex px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-[0.8rem] font-bold bg-terracotta-light text-terracotta mb-4">스파르타</div>
          <div class="space-y-2 mb-5">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[0.9rem]"><span class="text-brown">수업량</span><span class="font-semibold text-brown-dark">하루 10~12시간</span></div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[0.9rem]"><span class="text-brown">외출</span><span class="font-semibold text-brown-dark">평일 외출 금지</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="border-t border-beige-dark pt-5 space-y-2.5">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[0.85rem] text-brown leading-[1.5]"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brown-light shrink-0 mt-2"></div>의무 자습 + 단어 시험</div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[0.85rem] text-brown leading-[1.5]"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brown-light shrink-0 mt-2"></div>평일 외출 불가 (주말 가능)</div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[0.85rem] text-brown leading-[1.5]"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brown-light shrink-0 mt-2"></div>단기간 집중 학습에 최적</div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[0.85rem] text-brown leading-[1.5]"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brown-light shrink-0 mt-2"></div>강제성이 있어 자기관리 약한 분에게 추천</div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-5 pt-4 border-t border-beige-dark text-[0.82rem] font-medium text-terracotta">단기간 확실한 성과가 필요한 분</div>
        </div>
        <!-- 세미스파르타 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-[20px] p-7 border border-accent-green/30 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <div class="inline-flex px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-[0.8rem] font-bold bg-accent-green-light text-accent-green-dark mb-4">세미스파르타</div>
          <div class="space-y-2 mb-5">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[0.9rem]"><span class="text-brown">수업량</span><span class="font-semibold text-brown-dark">하루 8~10시간</span></div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[0.9rem]"><span class="text-brown">외출</span><span class="font-semibold text-brown-dark">평일 저녁 외출 가능</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="border-t border-beige-dark pt-5 space-y-2.5">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[0.85rem] text-brown leading-[1.5]"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brown-light shrink-0 mt-2"></div>수업 참여 의무 + 자율 복습</div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[0.85rem] text-brown leading-[1.5]"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brown-light shrink-0 mt-2"></div>평일 저녁 외출 가능 (통금 있음)</div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[0.85rem] text-brown leading-[1.5]"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brown-light shrink-0 mt-2"></div>학습과 생활의 균형</div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[0.85rem] text-brown leading-[1.5]"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brown-light shrink-0 mt-2"></div>가장 인기 있는 스타일</div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-5 pt-4 border-t border-beige-dark text-[0.82rem] font-medium text-accent-green-dark">학습과 여가를 균형 있게 즐기고 싶은 분</div>
        </div>
        <!-- 자율형 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-[20px] p-7 border border-beige-dark hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <div class="inline-flex px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-[0.8rem] font-bold bg-beige text-brown-dark mb-4">자율형</div>
          <div class="space-y-2 mb-5">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[0.9rem]"><span class="text-brown">수업량</span><span class="font-semibold text-brown-dark">하루 6~8시간</span></div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[0.9rem]"><span class="text-brown">외출</span><span class="font-semibold text-brown-dark">자유 외출</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="border-t border-beige-dark pt-5 space-y-2.5">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[0.85rem] text-brown leading-[1.5]"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brown-light shrink-0 mt-2"></div>수업 외 시간 완전 자율</div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[0.85rem] text-brown leading-[1.5]"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brown-light shrink-0 mt-2"></div>외출·외박 자유</div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[0.85rem] text-brown leading-[1.5]"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brown-light shrink-0 mt-2"></div>자기주도 학습 가능한 분에게 적합</div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[0.85rem] text-brown leading-[1.5]"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brown-light shrink-0 mt-2"></div>현지 문화 체험 병행 가능</div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-5 pt-4 border-t border-beige-dark text-[0.82rem] font-medium text-brown-dark">자기관리를 잘하는 분, 장기 연수자</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 3: 기숙형 어학원 -->
  <section id="section-2" class="py-20 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="reveal rounded-[20px] aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden order-last md:order-first">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1562774053-701939374585?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="어학원 캠퍼스 전경" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-terracotta-light text-terracotta px-3 py-1.5 rounded-2xl text-[0.75rem] font-semibold mb-4">POINT 03</div>
        <h2 class="text-[1.6rem] md:text-[2.2rem] font-extrabold tracking-tight text-brown-dark leading-[1.3]">
          기숙사 + 식사 + 수업<br /><span class="text-terracotta">올인원 시스템</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-5 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] text-brown">
          필리핀 어학원은 대부분 <strong>기숙사, 식당, 강의실이 한 캠퍼스</strong> 안에 있습니다. 숙소를 따로 구하거나 밥을 챙겨 먹을 걱정 없이 <strong>오직 공부에만 집중</strong>할 수 있어요.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-3">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-cream rounded-xl px-5 py-3.5 border border-beige-dark"><span class="text-xl shrink-0">🏠</span><span class="text-[0.9rem] text-brown-dark">기숙사와 강의실이 같은 건물, 통학 시간 제로</span></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-cream rounded-xl px-5 py-3.5 border border-beige-dark"><span class="text-xl shrink-0">🍽️</span><span class="text-[0.9rem] text-brown-dark">하루 3식 제공 (한식 위주), 식비 걱정 없음</span></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-cream rounded-xl px-5 py-3.5 border border-beige-dark"><span class="text-xl shrink-0">🧹</span><span class="text-[0.9rem] text-brown-dark">청소, 세탁 서비스 제공 (주 2~3회)</span></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-cream rounded-xl px-5 py-3.5 border border-beige-dark"><span class="text-xl shrink-0">👥</span><span class="text-[0.9rem] text-brown-dark">외국인 룸메이트와 자연스러운 영어 사용</span></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-cream rounded-xl px-5 py-3.5 border border-beige-dark"><span class="text-xl shrink-0">🛡️</span><span class="text-[0.9rem] text-brown-dark">한국인 매니저 상주, 생활 상담 가능</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 4: 합리적 비용 -->
  <section id="section-3" class="py-20 px-6 bg-brown-dark text-cream relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute -top-1/2 -right-[20%] w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(196,96,58,0.15)_0%,transparent_70%)] rounded-full"></div>
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto relative">
      <div class="reveal text-center mb-14">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-[rgba(74,140,92,0.2)] text-[#8FD4A0] px-3 py-1.5 rounded-2xl text-[0.75rem] font-semibold mb-4">POINT 04</div>
        <h2 class="text-[1.6rem] md:text-[2.2rem] font-extrabold tracking-tight text-cream leading-[1.3]">
          학비에 숙식비가 포함,<br /><span class="text-terracotta-light">타 국가 대비 절반 이하 비용</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.7] text-brown-light max-w-[600px] mx-auto">
          필리핀은 학비 자체가 저렴한 데다 숙식비까지 포함되어 있어<br />다른 영어권 국가와 비교하면 비용이 훨씬 합리적입니다.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <!-- 필리핀 -->
        <div class="rounded-[20px] p-7 backdrop-blur-[4px] border transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 bg-[rgba(196,96,58,0.15)] border-terracotta">
          <span class="inline-block bg-terracotta text-white px-3 py-0.5 rounded-[10px] text-[0.7rem] font-bold mb-3">추천</span>
          <div class="text-[1rem] font-bold text-cream mb-1">필리핀</div>
          <div class="text-[0.8rem] text-brown-light mb-4">8주 기준</div>
          <div class="text-[2rem] font-black text-cream tracking-tight">약 280만원~</div>
          <div class="text-[0.8rem] text-brown-light mt-1 mb-5">학비 + 기숙사 + 식사 포함</div>
          <div class="border-t border-white/10 pt-4 space-y-2">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[0.82rem] text-brown-light leading-[1.5]"><div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brown-light shrink-0 mt-2"></div>1:1 수업 4~6시간/일</div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[0.82rem] text-brown-light leading-[1.5]"><div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brown-light shrink-0 mt-2"></div>기숙사 + 3식 포함</div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[0.82rem] text-brown-light leading-[1.5]"><div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brown-light shrink-0 mt-2"></div>생활비 별도 (월 20~30만원)</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 호주·캐나다 -->
        <div class="rounded-[20px] p-7 backdrop-blur-[4px] border transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 bg-white/[0.06] border-white/10 hover:bg-white/10">
          <div class="text-[1rem] font-bold text-cream mb-1">호주 · 캐나다</div>
          <div class="text-[0.8rem] text-brown-light mb-4">8주 기준</div>
          <div class="text-[2rem] font-black text-cream tracking-tight">약 600~800만원</div>
          <div class="text-[0.8rem] text-brown-light mt-1 mb-5">학비만 (숙식 별도)</div>
          <div class="border-t border-white/10 pt-4 space-y-2">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[0.82rem] text-brown-light leading-[1.5]"><div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brown-light shrink-0 mt-2"></div>그룹 수업 15~20명</div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[0.82rem] text-brown-light leading-[1.5]"><div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brown-light shrink-0 mt-2"></div>홈스테이 별도 (월 100만원+)</div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[0.82rem] text-brown-light leading-[1.5]"><div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brown-light shrink-0 mt-2"></div>생활비 별도 (월 80~120만원)</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 미국·영국 -->
        <div class="rounded-[20px] p-7 backdrop-blur-[4px] border transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 bg-white/[0.06] border-white/10 hover:bg-white/10">
          <div class="text-[1rem] font-bold text-cream mb-1">미국 · 영국</div>
          <div class="text-[0.8rem] text-brown-light mb-4">8주 기준</div>
